subSubSection.paragraph:
Cephalothorax
(
Fig. 12A–C
): Carapace yellowish, with a broad yellow-brown pattern medially. Sternum yellowish. Labium brown. Chelicerae (
Fig. 15E, F
) brown, with six promarginal peg teeth and two retromarginal teeth.
